---
title: Orange-Thyme Pork Loin Steaks with Garlic Mash & Steamed Beans
description: We don’t know why, but pork with fruit is an endlessly inspiring combination! This seasonal twist is orange and thyme, which adds a fragrant and delicious finish to this simple and totally tasty supper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b6d00ebae08b5583c6acdc3-f0c84426.jpg
